value.0: Moonshaes is a faithful, to-scale recreation of the classic Forgotten Realms setting The Moonshae Isles, built in painstaking detail and with a plethora of static content and custom mechanics that bring the world to life. As part of the premier roleplaying community A Land Far Away (ALFA), our DMs seek to recreate the pen-and-paper DnD experience by producing fun and challenging scenarios for player characters to explore as well as an ongoing world narrative for players to participate in and shape. Visit www.alfanwn1.org for more info, and links to our Discord and custom music & portrait packs.
